e family of the victim. Details coming soon… Vanguard By Festus Ahon ASABA -TENSION heightened, Saturday in Asaba, the Delta State capital, following the kidnap of the Chairman of Nigeria Labour Congress, NLC in the State, Comrade Goodluck Ofobruku by gunmen at about 8pm. Vanguard gathered that the Labour leader was driving out, behind Immigration office along Ibusa on… July 5, 2020 In "News" Chairman of All Progressives Congress, APC, in Matazu Local Government Area of Katsina State, Alhaji Yusau Dissi, was reportedly abducted alongside nine others by gunmen in different attacks across the state. July 6, 2020 In "News" The police have confirmed the abduction of Mr. Goodluck Ofobruku, Chairman of Delta chapter of the Nigeria Labour Congress (NLC), on Saturday night in Asaba. July 5, 2020 In "News"